  <scopecontent id="aspace_c7a895903622fcafb6a4e91ffa5cc6d0">
    <head>COLLECTION DESCRIPTION</head>
<p>Transcripts of taped sessions of a conference on "Women Today" sponsored by the New York State College of Human Ecology (then the College of Home Economics), including transcript of a session on "The Black Woman in America"; memoranda; correspondence; schedules; agenda; and summaries and commentary on sessions.</p>  </scopecontent>
  <prefercite id="aspace_26c9162bb6d22f4b080e29de792f0f84">
